PN,37112
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1784558904
OL,3,CNew museum in country house reveals
OL,4,Csecrets of espionage during WWII
OL,6,FAfter the war, the House became a
OL,7,Fteacher training college, and
OL,8,Feventually part of MiddlesexUniversity
OL,9,Funtil 2012.
OL,11,FIn 2014, the idea for a museum came to
OL,12,Flight and later put in a planning
OL,13,Fapplication for redevelopment.
OL,15,FThe museum opens to the public on
OL,16,FTuesday 21 July.
OL,18,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,19,Four political experts are across all
OL,20,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,21,Fto the latest episode below...
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G12/12
